commit.title: WIP: [sphinx] Add warn option to coqtop directive.
commit.message:
WIP: [sphinx] Add warn option to coqtop directive.

By default Coq warnings are made fatal when building the manual.
If you want to show a command resulting in a warning, use the warn option.
